Description: Up for auction is this 2016 Ibanez RG652AHM Prestige in Nebula Green Burst. Made in Japan. It has mostly been kept at home for recording and practicing. Like any used guitar, there will me some wear on the frets, from normal use, but nothing that will give you any major issues. Frets still have plenty of life in them.
